title: 10/22/21 DPS Best Of
itunes:title: 10/22/21 DPS Best Of
description:
On today's Dan Patrick Show, DP discusses the rivalry between USC and Notre Dame with former Fighting Irish QB Brady Quinn. He shares what his favorite memories from playing in the rivalry were. Ross Tucker calls in to recap last night's game between the Browns and Broncos. What are the chances he thinks the Browns will give Baker a big contract. And NBC Soccer's Rebecca Lowe joins DP to talk all things soccer.
